{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6c38ec35-45b8-4f36-b647-748f4d805fbe",
    "name": "Course Platform API",
    "description": "Postman collection for the Course Platform backend. Suggested flow:\n1) Register + Login Instructor → Create Course (saves courseId)\n2) Create Lesson (saves lessonId)\n3) Register + Login Student → Enroll → Rate / Progress / Comments\n\nCollection variables: baseUrl, instructorToken, studentToken, courseId, lessonId.",
